spec_data.Name: libmikmod
spec_data.Description:
libmikmod is a library used by the mikmod MOD music file player for
UNIX-like systems. Supported file formats include MOD, STM, S3M, MTM,
XM, ULT and IT.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 31 Oct 2017 04:29:02 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A MOD music file player library
